{"fadeType":1,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["<size=51>「己を貫く」――と大先輩が言っていた<\/size>",1],["<size=51>私が信じていた、重桜と仲間たちを率いている、あの赤城先輩と加賀先輩が<\/size>",3],["<size=51>まさか、セイレーンと結託しているだなんて……<\/size>",5],["<size=51>あと「聖域」の件のあとも、頑張って調べていた<\/size> ",7],["<size=51>幸い、大先輩と長門様、陸奥様と江風が信用してくれた<\/size>",9],["<size=51>あの海域で出会った暁と山城はどうやら無事だけど<\/size>",11],["<size=51>みんな、あのときの出来事が記憶にないようで……<\/size>",13],["<size=51>この祭儀で、何もわからないかもしれない<\/size>",15],["<size=51>でも、それでも………<\/size>",17],["<size=51>…………<\/size>",19],["<size=51>――きっとなにかが、分かる気がする――<\/size>",21]]},{"sequence":[["",2]],"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"effects":[{"active":true,"name":"logo_sakura"}],"blackBg":true},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"数日前、とある海域にて","dir":1,"bgm":"story-6","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"bgmDelay":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"soundeffect":"event:\/battle\/boom2","effects":[{"active":false,"name":"logo_sakura"},{"active":true,"name":"miwu_01"}],"bgName":"bg_xinnong_cg3","flashin":{"delay":1.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"effect":[{"active":true,"name":"UIhuohua"}],"side":2,"say":"この時代に存在し得ない施設の残骸と、いたる所に残っている斬撃の痕跡が、この場所と、この場所を襲撃した存在の正体を示している。","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_xinnong_cg3","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"ここはセイレーンによって創造された「鏡面海域」――正確に言えば、「鏡面海域」だった場所だ。","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_xinnong_cg3","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"…うまく片付いた。拙者は次の場所に移動させてもらう","dir":1,"actorName":"？？？","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_xinnong_cg3","actor":900192},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"あら、久しぶりの客人ね。珍しいじゃない","dir":1,"actorName":"オブザーバー","paintingNoise":true,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_xinnong_cg3","actor":900012},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","